active dry yeast (a 1/4-ounce package)	2 1/4	teaspoons	
all-purpose flour	3	cups	
mild honey or sugar	1	tablespoon	
plus more for kneading and dusting			
table salt	1	tablespoon	
water	1/4	cup	
whole-wheat flour	1 1/2	cups	
medium bulgur (also called cracked wheat)	1/2	cup	
large egg	1		
unsalted butter	1	stick	
whole milk	1 1/2	cups	
flaky sea salt (preferably maldon)	1 1/2	tablespoons	
